text: Fatkullino () is a rural locality (a village) in Ulu-Telyaksky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 48 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 66 km from Iglino and 4 km from Ulu-Telyak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Fatkullino
